posting_body: ['5th, Top Floor Studio', '* $2,495/month annual lease', '* Shared laundry', "* Parking available for an add'l fee", '* Small pets considered', '*', 'Available:', 'Now', 'OPEN HOUSE: Please call', 'show contact info', 'Address:494 27th', 'Avenue #58', 'Large, fifth, top floor studio in Central Richmond.', 'Heat is steam.', 'Main room is sizeable.', 'Floors are hardwood except in bath.', 'Kitchen is around a corner, parallel to the main room.', 'It has space for a modest dining arrangement in front of the window.', 'Building has a shared, coin-operated laundry.', "Parking in the building's garage is available for an additional fee.", 'Small pets considered.', 'Walk Score is 95.', 'Shopping and dining on Geary Street is less than a block away, just one block to the same on Clement Street.', 'Golden Gate Park is just two blocks away.', 'Transit Score is 72.', 'Bus lines 1, 29, 31 and 38 are within easy walking distance.', "Tenant pays a one-time broker's fee.", 'Everest Mwamba', 'DRE# 01717299', 'Kenney & Everest Real Estate', 'DRE# 01984640', 'show contact info', 'office', 'Apply at KenneyandEverest .', 'com', 'Leasing and Real Estate: Our Family Business for Over 100 Years.', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'Please note: Images used are from a similar unit on the same floor.']
